/build_*/
/build-win*/
/build_win*/
/install/
/install_*/
/install-win*/
/install_win*/

# CMake, Ninja, and dependency build byproducts
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/compile_commands.json
**/.ninja_deps
**/.ninja_log
**/_deps/

